'''Dominic Armato''' (born [[November 18]], [[1976]]) is an American voice actor who has worked on several ''Star Wars'' video games.

He is best known as providing the voice of [[Guybrush Threepkiller|Guybrush Threepwood]] in the [[Wikipedia:Monkey Island|Monkey Island]] games.

